287
00:19:07,360 --> 00:19:08,400
Yet, you have the audacity

288
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:10,120
to sulk,

289
00:19:10,600 --> 00:19:11,880
give me the silent treatment,

290
00:19:12,520 --> 00:19:13,600
and take your blanket

291
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:16,160
and move to the massage room upstairs.

292
00:19:16,360 --> 00:19:19,317
That's what I call failing the test.

293
00:19:19,400 --> 00:19:21,157
You... You are the one who failed.

294
00:19:21,240 --> 00:19:22,040
Fine.

295
00:19:22,280 --> 00:19:23,120
I failed.

296
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:29,520
Who says I crumbled faster

297
00:19:29,960 --> 00:19:30,880
than Tou Tou?

298
00:19:32,480 --> 00:19:33,280
Actually...

299
00:19:36,080 --> 00:19:38,200
Actually, I never doubted you at all.

300
00:19:38,880 --> 00:19:40,920
I knew Tou Tou isn't your daughter.

301
00:19:41,800 --> 00:19:42,800
I was just upset that

302
00:19:43,280 --> 00:19:44,797
you put me in an embarrassing position

303
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:46,120
in front of so many people.

304
00:19:46,640 --> 00:19:47,760
You didn't respect me.

305
00:19:51,760 --> 00:19:52,720
All right, all right.

306
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:57,240
(Jiangzhou People's Hospital)

307
00:20:16,120 --> 00:20:16,920
What's the matter?

308
00:20:17,400 --> 00:20:18,800
Missing your master?

309
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:29,280
I miss them.

310
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:31,800
Them?

311
00:20:34,360 --> 00:20:36,080
So, there is someone else
that you miss.

312
00:20:38,040 --> 00:20:38,840
Look at you,

313
00:20:39,360 --> 00:20:40,560
you insisted on hiding here

314
00:20:41,320 --> 00:20:42,520
when you could have gone home.

315
00:20:43,280 --> 00:20:44,080
Now this is great.

316
00:20:45,040 --> 00:20:46,397
Even if you want to go back,

317
00:20:46,480 --> 00:20:47,360
you can't.

318
00:20:48,800 --> 00:20:50,080
I don't have a home.

319
00:20:54,760 --> 00:20:56,000
Look at you,

320
00:20:57,120 --> 00:20:58,520
your master treats you so well.

321
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:00,400
You are so ungrateful.

322
00:21:01,840 --> 00:21:03,797
It's precisely because
my master treats me well

323
00:21:03,880 --> 00:21:05,557
that I can't leave.

324
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:06,797
Can Ms Shen take care of

325
00:21:06,880 --> 00:21:08,520
both you and Grandma alone?

326
00:21:13,440 --> 00:21:14,240
I say,

327
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:17,240
has your master not contacted you
for several days?

328
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:19,840
They are all busy.

329
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:27,000
Looks like your master has abandoned me.

330
00:21:33,360 --> 00:21:34,160
Nephew No. 2,

331
00:21:35,120 --> 00:21:35,920
don't worry.

332
00:21:36,360 --> 00:21:39,120
As long as I'm around,
your life won't be in danger.

333
00:21:41,400 --> 00:21:42,520
I say,

334
00:21:43,920 --> 00:21:46,360
although you performed acupuncture on me

335
00:21:46,760 --> 00:21:48,440
under your master's guidance,

336
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:49,797
it is also

337
00:21:49,880 --> 00:21:52,120
under my guidance and supervision.

338
00:21:53,280 --> 00:21:54,157
I think

339
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:56,440
you should get a new master.

340
00:21:56,840 --> 00:21:58,677
Don't be stubbornly attached
to one side.

341
00:21:58,760 --> 00:21:59,597
Starting from tomorrow,

342
00:21:59,680 --> 00:22:02,640
you will ask to be my disciple.

343
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:06,120
Don't underestimate me

344
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:07,320
and think I'm incapable.

345
00:22:07,720 --> 00:22:09,760
Even though your master is renowned,

346
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:13,120
don't forget that I am also
a influential figure in Jiangzhou.

347
00:22:15,240 --> 00:22:16,600
Even if I can't be number one,

348
00:22:17,120 --> 00:22:18,437
I can at least

349
00:22:18,520 --> 00:22:19,440
be number two.

350
00:22:21,000 --> 00:22:22,400
I'm only telling you this,

351
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:23,840
if anyone else

352
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:25,600
wants to become my disciple,

353
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:28,000
I won't even bother.

354
00:22:28,960 --> 00:22:30,760
I see how dedicated you have been

355
00:22:31,160 --> 00:22:33,000
taking care of me these days.

356
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:36,280
That's why I'm willing
to let go of the grudge,

357
00:22:36,880 --> 00:22:38,360
and I don't mean you,

358
00:22:38,640 --> 00:22:40,240
I mean the grudge against your master,

359
00:22:40,800 --> 00:22:42,560
and accept you as my student.

360
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:44,680
Don't hesitate anymore.

361
00:22:52,640 --> 00:22:54,760
That's quite a tempting offer.

362
00:22:59,000 --> 00:22:59,917
I've made up my mind.

363
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:01,240
Made up your mind about what?

364
00:23:04,040 --> 00:23:05,400
Once I'm out of the hospital,

365
00:23:06,960 --> 00:23:08,800
I will kowtow to Senior Master.

366
00:23:09,240 --> 00:23:10,797
If he could teach
the two of you so well,

367
00:23:10,880 --> 00:23:12,800
then teaching me should not
be a problem, right?

368
00:23:13,040 --> 00:23:14,917
It's settled, I will kowtow
to Senior Master.

369
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:16,000
Child,

370
00:23:16,200 --> 00:23:18,400
I don't admire anyone else,
but I truly admire you.

371
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:20,480
Even when you turn someone down,

372
00:23:21,040 --> 00:23:23,080
you manage to do it tactfully
without hurting our relationship.

373
00:23:28,360 --> 00:23:30,280
Hello, everyone. I'm Dr Peng.

374
00:23:30,480 --> 00:23:32,280
I will teach everyone how to make

375
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:34,517
Fried Rice Tea and Egg Dumplings
in today's live stream.

376
00:23:34,600 --> 00:23:35,400
Let's start with

377
00:23:35,640 --> 00:23:37,640
the Egg Dumplings.

378
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:41,277
(Class representative, Xiao Hong,
are you ready?)

379
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:42,640
All ready to go.

380
00:23:43,640 --> 00:23:45,200
First, let's put oil

381
00:23:46,280 --> 00:23:47,440
in the pan

382
00:23:47,600 --> 00:23:49,120
and evenly preheat it.

383
00:23:50,240 --> 00:23:53,120
Then, we'll add
the previously beaten eggs.

384
00:23:54,120 --> 00:23:55,000
As for the dumplings,

385
00:23:55,120 --> 00:23:57,760
I've chosen Shrimp Supreme Dumpling.

386
00:23:58,200 --> 00:23:59,677
These dumplings have

387
00:23:59,760 --> 00:24:01,080
whole and large shrimp inside.

388
00:24:01,520 --> 00:24:04,397
Shrimp meat contains abundant protein

389
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:07,360
and essential trace elements
needed by the human body.

390
00:24:07,520 --> 00:24:10,240
So, we should eat more shrimp meat.

391
00:24:12,520 --> 00:24:15,120
The heat of the oil is about right.
Now we can add the dumplings.

392
00:24:17,760 --> 00:24:20,080
Cook them on low heat for three minutes.

393
00:24:20,360 --> 00:24:22,040
Remember, it must be low heat.

394
00:24:25,040 --> 00:24:25,840
Careful!

395
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:28,397
This is very normal.

396
00:24:28,480 --> 00:24:29,840
You know that, right?

397
00:24:30,219 --> 00:24:31,296
The eggs fried this way

398
00:24:31,400 --> 00:24:32,920
taste especially good, you know?

399
00:24:35,760 --> 00:24:37,877
Class representative, Xiao Hong,
was just a little impatient.

400
00:24:37,960 --> 00:24:39,880
We were supposed to add the eggs later.

401
00:24:41,253 --> 00:24:43,636
(Don't criticise her anymore.
Or she won't be frying the pan anymore,)

402
00:24:43,720 --> 00:24:44,792
(she will be toasting you.)

403
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:46,800
Oh, my God.

404
00:24:54,160 --> 00:24:54,960
Where is it?

405
00:24:55,760 --> 00:24:57,280
On the right. Bingfeng acupoint.

406
00:24:57,760 --> 00:24:58,560
Tianzong acupoint.

407
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:00,800
And around Xinshu acupoint.

408
00:25:04,640 --> 00:25:08,080
Is that really important whether
or not Tou Tou is my daughter?

409
00:25:09,240 --> 00:25:10,400
One day as a teacher,

410
00:25:11,360 --> 00:25:12,600
a lifetime as a father.

411
00:25:14,080 --> 00:25:16,960
Isn't that how it is
in our ancient Chinese culture?

412
00:25:18,240 --> 00:25:19,320
The master

413
00:25:20,360 --> 00:25:21,720
is like a father.

414
00:25:23,400 --> 00:25:24,320
It's different.

415
00:25:28,480 --> 00:25:30,240
You really can't accept Tou Tou

416
00:25:30,880 --> 00:25:32,520
as a member of our family?

417
00:25:35,520 --> 00:25:36,317
I can't accept that

418
00:25:36,400 --> 00:25:37,920
you have someone else in your heart.

419
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:41,640
Why have I been together

420
00:25:42,120 --> 00:25:43,600
with you for so many years?

421
00:25:45,240 --> 00:25:46,800
You always donate money

422
00:25:46,960 --> 00:25:48,840
and visit other cities to
provide medical support.

423
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:50,637
I never complained

424
00:25:50,720 --> 00:25:51,800
and fully supported you.

425
00:25:52,320 --> 00:25:53,640
But you haven't treated me well.

426
00:25:54,640 --> 00:25:56,480
Other couples enjoy romance and love,

427
00:25:57,000 --> 00:25:58,037
but with you,

428
00:25:58,120 --> 00:25:59,197
it's always about hardships

429
00:25:59,280 --> 00:26:00,440
and sacrifices.

430
00:26:03,000 --> 00:26:05,080
I've been the one holding
this family together.

431
00:26:06,040 --> 00:26:06,840
In the end,

432
00:26:07,120 --> 00:26:09,640
I can't even get your loyalty,
which is the most basic thing.

433
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:11,040
What should I do?

434
00:26:12,840 --> 00:26:14,440
You've destroyed my trust.

435
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:16,880
Now that I've told you the truth.

436
00:26:17,160 --> 00:26:18,800
Have I earned your trust again?

437
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:20,280
No.

438
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:27,677
There's something that
has been weighing on my mind,

439
00:26:27,760 --> 00:26:29,040
and I want to ask you directly.

440
00:26:30,240 --> 00:26:32,760
Today, you must give me
an honest answer.

441
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:40,000
What's the deal

442
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:42,520
between you and Little Lark?

443
00:26:45,120 --> 00:26:46,480
What's your relationship?

444
00:26:50,600 --> 00:26:52,280
I only said that I was Tou Tou's father.

445
00:26:52,520 --> 00:26:54,600
Now you're even trying
to find her mother for me?

446
00:27:03,400 --> 00:27:05,200
(The fact that you've been
searching for her all these years)

447
00:27:05,480 --> 00:27:06,600
(shows that)

448
00:27:07,120 --> 00:27:08,600
(you can't forget about her, right?)

449
00:27:09,040 --> 00:27:09,840
(If she hadn't)

450
00:27:10,160 --> 00:27:11,720
(dropped out of school back then,)

451
00:27:12,640 --> 00:27:14,720
(maybe we wouldn't have
started our relationship.)

452
00:27:15,720 --> 00:27:17,000
So, your trust

453
00:27:17,640 --> 00:27:19,960
was built on doubt all along?

454
00:27:21,760 --> 00:27:23,400
Have you always had her in your heart?

455
00:27:25,640 --> 00:27:26,440
Have you?

456
00:27:29,760 --> 00:27:30,560
Yes.

457
00:27:32,280 --> 00:27:33,160
Listen,

458
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:37,120
it's not what you imagine.

459
00:27:38,760 --> 00:27:41,640
Do you know why Little Lark
dropped out of school?

460
00:27:42,160 --> 00:27:43,360
It's because of me.

461
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:49,400
I made a mistake

462
00:27:51,120 --> 00:27:53,120
that caused her to lose
her hearing in both ears.

463
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:58,800
You don't know this,

464
00:28:00,400 --> 00:28:02,040
but the hardships I faced on my journey

465
00:28:03,160 --> 00:28:05,240
to learn TCM knowledge

466
00:28:06,720 --> 00:28:07,637
were unimaginable

467
00:28:07,720 --> 00:28:09,317
for descendants of TCM families

468
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:10,560
like you.

469
00:28:11,480 --> 00:28:13,437
In order to learn the essence of TCM,

470
00:28:13,520 --> 00:28:15,000
I had studied under many masters.

471
00:28:17,760 --> 00:28:19,040
(Now it seems that)

472
00:28:19,960 --> 00:28:21,240
(some of those masters)

473
00:28:21,880 --> 00:28:23,520
(had limitation in their knowledge.)

474
00:28:24,360 --> 00:28:25,520
(At that time,)

475
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:30,280
(I didn't have the ability
to discern their shortcomings.)

476
00:28:31,040 --> 00:28:32,360
I will insert the needle now.

477
00:28:44,040 --> 00:28:44,840
(I didn't know)

478
00:28:45,360 --> 00:28:47,000
the gravity of it.

479
00:28:48,480 --> 00:28:49,440
I was bold

480
00:28:50,240 --> 00:28:51,040
but lacked

481
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:54,240
a very good teacher

482
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:55,677
to guide me.

483
00:28:55,760 --> 00:28:57,520
I was just experimenting
on my treatments.

484
00:28:59,240 --> 00:29:00,560
You can't imagine

485
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:03,400
how innocent and naive

486
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:05,360
those people were

487
00:29:07,760 --> 00:29:08,920
(in those days.)

488
00:29:11,040 --> 00:29:11,920
(She believed in me)

489
00:29:13,360 --> 00:29:14,440
(and let me treat her.)

490
00:29:30,360 --> 00:29:31,160
And the result...

491
00:29:34,120 --> 00:29:35,120
What happened?

492
00:29:37,640 --> 00:29:38,440
The result was...

493
00:29:48,840 --> 00:29:50,200
She became deaf in both ears.

494
00:29:50,880 --> 00:29:53,520
At that time,
I thought it was temporary.

495
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:55,720
We sought treatment

496
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:58,560
from both TCM and Western doctors.

497
00:30:00,120 --> 00:30:01,400
Six months passed,

498
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:04,600
and it was too late to change anything.

499
00:30:12,280 --> 00:30:13,680
Stop blaming yourself.

500
00:30:14,280 --> 00:30:15,680
Little Lark left without telling anyone

501
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:17,640
because she didn't want
to see you like this.

502
00:30:18,560 --> 00:30:20,960
She even packed her stuff by herself.

503
00:30:22,120 --> 00:30:22,920
Study well.

504
00:30:23,640 --> 00:30:24,920
The only thing you can do

505
00:30:25,520 --> 00:30:27,360
to atone for it
is to become a great doctor.

506
00:30:40,520 --> 00:30:43,037
My heart always aches
when I think about her,

507
00:30:43,120 --> 00:30:44,000
you know?

508
00:30:44,840 --> 00:30:45,920
If there's anyone

509
00:30:48,913 --> 00:30:50,913
I've failed in my life,

510
00:30:52,273 --> 00:30:53,553
it's Little Lark.

511
00:30:58,246 --> 00:30:59,327
It was a mistake,

512
00:31:00,840 --> 00:31:02,677
but in a way, it was also a good thing.

513
00:31:02,760 --> 00:31:03,960
Because of her,

514
00:31:04,832 --> 00:31:07,072
I have truly devoted myself to studying.

515
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:11,277
I want to learn pure TCM

516
00:31:11,360 --> 00:31:13,040
and become the best doctor.

517
00:31:13,240 --> 00:31:15,120
No matter where she is,

518
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:16,880
I will find her.

519
00:31:18,480 --> 00:31:20,640
With my current understanding of TCM,

520
00:31:22,240 --> 00:31:23,280
I want to take a chance.

521
00:31:30,160 --> 00:31:30,960
I know

522
00:31:32,880 --> 00:31:34,480
you have always approached TCM

523
00:31:35,520 --> 00:31:36,437
with caution

524
00:31:36,520 --> 00:31:37,760
and meticulousness,

525
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:41,360
and treated patients

526
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:43,480
with utmost care.

527
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:45,760
I didn't realise

528
00:31:46,120 --> 00:31:48,400
that it was Little Lark
who made you who you are today.

529
00:31:51,240 --> 00:31:53,760
Then, did you see her
at the class reunion?

530
00:31:55,120 --> 00:31:55,920
Yes, I did.

531
00:31:58,480 --> 00:32:00,040
She is still as cheerful as ever.

532
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:03,960
She didn't utter a word
of resentment towards me.

533
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:08,240
Didn't you treat her?

534
00:32:10,240 --> 00:32:11,480
I couldn't convince her.

535
00:32:12,400 --> 00:32:14,320
She said she had given up on treatment.

536
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:17,360
She has adapted to the quiet world.

537
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:22,160
I feel so regretful.

538
00:32:30,840 --> 00:32:31,640
Xin Zheng...

539
00:32:35,120 --> 00:32:35,920
When we...

540
00:32:37,120 --> 00:32:38,800
When we leave Wuhan,

541
00:32:39,600 --> 00:32:40,920
bring me to her.

542
00:32:41,760 --> 00:32:42,880
I will convince her.

543
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:44,760
I will treat her, okay?

544
00:32:48,120 --> 00:32:48,920
Okay.

545
00:32:54,280 --> 00:32:55,080
Let's seal it.

546
00:32:56,080 --> 00:32:57,480
You are my dearest wife.

547
00:33:00,640 --> 00:33:02,640
But I'm still mad at you.

548
00:33:03,600 --> 00:33:04,960
I mean,

549
00:33:08,240 --> 00:33:09,960
something this huge

550
00:33:11,160 --> 00:33:12,320
has been weighed

551
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:15,360
on your heart for decades.

552
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:17,920
Yet you didn't even tell your wife.

553
00:33:19,280 --> 00:33:20,400
You just didn't...

554
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:22,320
You just didn't trust me.

555
00:33:23,480 --> 00:33:24,880
Telling you

556
00:33:25,840 --> 00:33:27,197
would only make one more person

557
00:33:27,280 --> 00:33:30,000
carry the guilt in this world.

558
00:33:33,960 --> 00:33:35,760
Guilt doesn't solve anything.

559
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:41,680
The only thing I could do
is to keep learning

560
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:44,640
and improving myself.

561
00:33:45,760 --> 00:33:47,640
I may have a chance
to change the result.

562
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:52,280
But

563
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:56,240
this big rock must be so heavy
in your heart.

564
00:33:57,240 --> 00:33:59,160
How many things have you kept inside?

565
00:34:02,360 --> 00:34:03,760
Now you understand

566
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:06,277
why I've been so strict

567
00:34:06,360 --> 00:34:07,640
with Tian Zhen.

568
00:34:10,520 --> 00:34:12,080
While others praise him,

569
