659
00:39:13,520 --> 00:39:15,400
You're just too cunning.

660
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:17,840
What's wrong with being cunning?

661
00:39:18,160 --> 00:39:19,280
Unlike you,

662
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:22,520
whose mind is so easy to read.

663
00:39:23,840 --> 00:39:24,637
Now you understand

664
00:39:24,720 --> 00:39:27,040
why your father passed on
the position to me

