00:39:52,800 --> 00:39:53,760
Do you understand now?

674
00:39:54,560 --> 00:39:56,080
You don't feel jealous now, do you?

675
00:39:57,600 --> 00:39:59,000
Am I the jealous one?

676
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:00,760
I am.

